summary: A skeleton that makes males appear buffer in all armors
descriptionHtml:
This mod is more slight than anything else, but I like it so I figured I would upload it. It basically makes males buffer by modding skeletons. Only works for males.

Installation: Merge the data folder with the existing one. If it asks you to replace skeleton.nif, it WILL conflict with a mod that you currently have downloaded. But it will only conflict in the sense that it will change the appearence. I can\'t see it doing any more than that.

Known Issues: None that I know of.

Thats kind of it. enjoy!
author: Koechophe
